location.fullValue: Residence One Plan, Saddle Point : Whispering Hills

data.description: This luxury home is in the prestigious Coronado section of Seven Hills on the golf course. Seven Hills is a 55+ senior community located in Hemet, CA. This house is a Plan 4 which is the largest and most sought-after floor plan. Three bedrooms, three baths, a see-through fireplace, a custom-enclosed patio, and an oversized garage are just a few of the features. High ceilings, plantation shutters, stained glass accent windows, and a well-appointed kitchen make living convenient yet cozy. Excellent condition and sparkling clean home. Upgraded and ready to move in. Near new flooring and carpet, 15K upgrade step-in master bathtub (2021), plantation shutters, and custom stained glass in the entryway. Upgraded 18K, HVAC system. Upgrades to the sprinkler and drip system. Nicely landscaped, including grapefruit, tangerine, and orange trees. SECURITY FEATURE- The home comes fully equipped with ADT home security systems - strategically placed sensors throughout the home, so every area is covered in a respective zone. All equipment is installed and stays with the home. New owner only has to set up their account.     ***The Seven Hills Members' Club is optional and includes a pool, spa, billiard room, card room, etc., and is great for socializing. The Seven Hills Golf Course is public and has a popular clubhouse with a well-equipped pro shop, as well as a bar, dining room, and snack counter. There is an active men's and ladies' club.***
